lead_paragraph: The Dickensian fog obscuring Wembley's arch hardly looked a portent of a golden era for England's national team as new manager Gareth Southgate spent his first day in the job trying to provide some cheer on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Southgate Talks of Great Expectations Amid the Gloom
